    "fullUrl" : "https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/sas/ValueSet/sas-valueset-typeconsultation",
    "resource" : {
      "resourceType" : "ValueSet",
      "text" : {
        "status" : "generated",
        "div" : "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet </b></p><p style=\"border: black 1px dotted; background-color: #EEEEEE; padding: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px\">Expansion based on <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/6.0.0/CodeSystem-v3-ActCode.html\">codesystem ActCode v9.0.0 (CodeSystem)</a></p><p>This value set contains 3 concepts</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>System</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><a name=\"x-http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-ActCode-AMB\"> </a>\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/6.0.0/CodeSystem-v3-ActCode.html#v3-ActCode-AMB\">AMB</a></td><td>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-ActCode</td><td>Consultation au cabinet</td><td><div><p>A comprehensive term for health care provided in a healthcare facility (e.g. a practitioneraTMs office, clinic setting, or hospital) on a nonresident basis. The term ambulatory usually implies that the patient has come to the location and is not assigned to a bed. Sometimes referred to as an outpatient encounter.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><a name=\"x-http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-ActCode-HH\"> </a>\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/6.0.0/CodeSystem-v3-ActCode.html#v3-ActCode-HH\">HH</a></td><td>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-ActCode</td><td>Consultation à domicile</td><td><div><p>Healthcare encounter that takes place in the residence of the patient or a designee</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><a name=\"x-http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-ActCode-VR\"> </a>\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/6.0.0/CodeSystem-v3-ActCode.html#v3-ActCode-VR\">VR</a></td><td>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-ActCode</td><td>Téléconsultation</td><td><div><p>A patient encounter where the patient and the practitioner(s) are not in the same physical location. Examples include telephone conference, email exchange, robotic surgery, and televideo conference.</p>\n</div></td></tr></table></div>"
